What if you could get involved with digital evangelism? You can! It is not just for pastors and leaders, it is a call for each of us. Find out how at the launch of Adventist Teams. Click below to sign up.

https://adventistteams.org/?lang=en

YouTube: https://youtube.com/c/AdventistOrgChurch
